          "COMMENT": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "Protons possessing energies from 16 MeV and above are",
                " studied.  Data relating to the excitation functions,",
                " angular  distributions  and  np coincidences suggest",
                " that the probability for formation of highly excited",
                " states  in the He-5 and Li-5 nuclei as a result of a",
                " single-particle reaction  on the Li-6 nucleus should",
                " be quite high."
              ]
            }
          ],
